'''堤喀'''（{{lang-en|Tyche}}）是[[太阳系|太阳系]][[奥尔特云|奥尔特云]]内的一颗假设的[[气态巨行星|气态巨行星]]的昵称。[[路易斯安那大学拉斐特分校|路易斯安那大学拉斐特分校]]的天文学家{{link-en|约翰·马泰塞|John Matese}}和{{link-en|丹尼尔·惠特迈尔|Daniel Whitmire}}<ref>{{Cite news|last = Rodgers|first = Paul|title = Up telescope! Search begins for giant new planet|newspaper = The Independent|date = 2011-02-13|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/up-telescope-search-begins-for-giant-new-planet-2213119.html|accessdate = 2011-02-26|archive-date = 2011-12-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111210081110/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/up-telescope-search-begins-for-giant-new-planet-2213119.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name='Space'>{{Cite news|first = Natalie|last = Wolchover|title = Article: Astronomers Doubt Giant Planet 'Tyche' Exists in Our Solar System|date = 2011-02-15|url = http://www.space.com/10863-mystery-planet-tyche-debate.html|work = Space.com|accessdate = 2011-02-26|archive-date = 2012-07-22|archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/69M5ur24c?url=http://www.space.com/10863-mystery-planet-tyche-debate.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>曾多次发表声明表示，基于长周期彗星运行轨道的不规则性，他们发现了该天体存在的证据。他们提到，假如堤喀的确存在，那么应能在[[美國國家航空暨太空總署|美國國家航空暨太空總署]]的[[廣域紅外線巡天探測衛星|廣域紅外線巡天探測衛星]]（WISE）望远镜观测到的数据中找到它。<ref name="MateseWhitmire2011">{{Cite journal | title=Persistent evidence of a jovian mass solar companion in the Oort cloud | last1=Matese | first1=John J. | last2=Whitmire | first2=Daniel P. | journal=Icarus | year=2011 | volume=211 | issue=2 | pages=926-938 | doi=10.1016/j.icarus.2010.11.009 | url=http://arxiv.org/PS_cache/arxiv/pdf/1004/1004.4584v1.pdf | id={{arxiv|1004.4584}} | access-date=2011-02-26 | archive-date=2021-01-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127173529/http://arxiv.org/PS_cache/arxiv/pdf/1004/1004.4584v1.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，一些天文学家对此表示怀疑<ref>{{cite web|title=Astronomers Doubt Giant Planet 'Tyche' Exists in Our Solar System|author=Natalie Wolchover|publisher=space.com|year=2011|url=http://www.space.com/10863-mystery-planet-tyche-debate.html|accessdate=2011-02-19|archive-date=2012-07-22|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69M5ur24c?url=http://www.space.com/10863-mystery-planet-tyche-debate.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BadAstronomy">{{Cite news|last = Plait|first = Phil|title = No, there’s no proof of a giant planet in the outer Solar System|newspaper = Discovery Magazine|date = 2011-02-14|url = http://blogs.discovermagazine.com/badastronomy/2011/02/14/no-theres-no-proof-of-a-giant-planet-in-the-outer-solar-system/#more-28256|accessdate = 2011-02-26|archive-date = 2016-04-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160416222414/http://blogs.discovermagazine.com/badastronomy/2011/02/14/no-theres-no-proof-of-a-giant-planet-in-the-outer-solar-system/#more-28256|dead-url = no}}</ref>，得花两到三年时间去分析数据，以确认WISE是否的确观测到了这颗行星的存在。<ref name="WISE">{{cite web
