== 历史 ==
1999年，基于[[长周期彗星|长周期彗星]]的起源点在观察上存在偏差的现象，马泰塞首次提出该行星存在的假设。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Continuing Evidence of an Impulsive Component of Oort Cloud Cometary Flux|first1=John J.|last1=Matese|first2=Jack J.|last2=Lissauer|work=University of Louisiana at Lafayette, and NASA Ames Research Center|url=http://www.ucs.louisiana.edu/~jjm9638/acm2002/acm2002_05_06.pdf|date=2002-05-06|accessdate=2011-02-26|archive-date=2012-07-22|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69M5wRFFo?url=http://www.ucs.louisiana.edu/~jjm9638/acm2002/acm2002_05_06.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>和通常认为的从随机点划过天空的看法不同，马泰塞得出了这些点聚集的范围偏向于[[黄道|黄道]]的结论。这种聚集现象的一种解释是，一颗至少与[[木星|木星]]一样大的未知天体扰乱了彗星运行的轨道，这颗天体有可能是[[褐矮星|褐矮星]]。这颗假设行星（或太阳的伴星）应该位于[[奥尔特云|奥尔特云]]的外围。<ref>{{Cite journal |first= John B. |last= Murray |title= Arguments for the Presence of a Distant Large Undiscovered Solar System Planet |journal= Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society |year= 1999 |volume= 309 |issue= 1 |pages= 31–34 |url= http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1999MNRAS.309...31M |laysource= Houston Chronicle |laysummary= http://www.chron.com/content/interactive/space/astronomy/news/1999/solarsys/991012.html |laydate= 1999-10-11 |doi= 10.1046/j.1365-8711.1999.02806.x |access-date= 2011-02-26 |archive-date= 2019-10-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191014223034/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1999mnras.309...31M |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |first1= John J. |last1= Matese |first2= Patrick  G. |last2= Whitman |first3= Daniel P . |last3= Whitmire |title= Cometary Evidence of a Massive Body in the Outer Oort Clouds |journal= Icarus |year= 1999 |volume= 141 |pages= 354 |doi= 10.1006/icar.1999.6177 |url= http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1999Icar..141..354M |access-date= 2011-02-26 |archive-date= 2019-09-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190913005056/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1999Icar..141..354M |dead-url= no }}</ref>他认为这样的天体也许还能够解释[[外海王星天体|外海王星天体]][[小行星90377|赛德娜]]的奇特轨道。<ref>{{cite journal|title=A Widebinary Solar Companion as a Possible Origin of Sedna-like Objects|first1=John J.|last1=Matese|first2=Daniel P.|last2=Whitmire|first3=Jack J.|last3=Lissauer|journal=Earth, Moon, and Planets|volume=97|issue=3-4|pages=459–470|year=2006|doi=10.1007/s11038-006-9078-6|url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/87v1p11t23832736/|accessdate=2010-08-17|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190916000001/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11038-006-9078-6|archive-date=2019-09-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>然而当时他的样本量太小而无法得出结论。<ref name="BadAstronomy"/>

== 轨道 ==
惠特迈尔和马泰塞推测这颗假设行星的轨道大约在[[海王星|海王星]]轨道位置的500倍之处，亦即离太阳有约15,000[[天文单位|天文单位]]远，将近四分之一[[光年|光年]]。据估计，[[奥尔特云|奥尔特云]]的边界应在50,000天文单位外，因此该天体依然位于奥尔特云内，其轨道周期约为180万年。<ref>{{cite web|title=Orbital period of a planet at a distance of 15000 AU with a circular orbit|url=http://www.calctool.org/CALC/phys/astronomy/planet_orbit|accessdate=2011-02-26|archive-date=2018-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003000218/http://www.calctool.org/CALC/phys/astronomy/planet_orbit|dead-url=no}}</ref>较早的[[红外天文卫星|红外天文卫星]]（IRAS）的一次失败搜寻显示5倍[[木星质量|木星质量]]天体的距离必须大于10,000天文单位。<ref name="MateseWhitmire2011"/>这样一颗行星旋转的平面与我们的不同，<ref name="UL">{{cite web |date=2011-02-14 |title=Have UL Physicists Identified a New Planet? |publisher=University of Louisiana |url=http://ultoday.com/node/3076 |accessdate=2011-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801125628/http://ultoday.com/node/3076 |archive-date=2015-08-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>并且有可能形成远距双星的轨道。<ref name="MateseWhitmire2011"/>这颗远距双星有可能是在星团解体时被捕获的。<ref name="MateseWhitmire2011"/>

